---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | AI Agency School">
  <div class="bg-black min-h-screen pt-24 pb-20">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative py-20">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8 border-b border-gold-500/30 pb-6">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-gold max-w-none text-neutral-300">
          <p class="font-bold text-white">Effective Date: January 1st, 2025</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-white mb-8">Last Updated: January 1st, 2025</p>

          <p class="mb-6">
            Altcutm LLC ("we," "us," or "our") operates AI Agency School (the "Service"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our Service.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-8">
            By using the Service, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">a) Personal Information You Provide</h3>
          <p>When you register, subscribe, or interact with the Service, we may collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number (optional, for WhatsApp support)</li>
            <li>Payment information (processed securely by Stripe; we do not store full card details)</li>
            <li>Business details (optional, e.g., agency name, website)</li>
            <li>Communication data (emails, support messages, course feedback)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">b) Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <p>When you access the Service, we may automatically collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Device information: IP address, browser type, operating system</li>
            <li>Usage data: Pages viewed, time spent, clickstream data</li>
            <li>Cookies and tracking technologies: See Section 8 below</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-2">c) Information from Third Parties</h3>
          <p>We may receive information from:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Stripe: Payment and transaction data</li>
            <li>Analytics providers: Google Analytics, Mixpanel, or similar</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Provide the Service: Process subscriptions, deliver content, manage your account</li>
            <li>Communicate: Send course updates, support responses, newsletters</li>
            <li>Process payments: Charge subscription fees, handle refunds (via Stripe)</li>
            <li>Improve the Service: Analyze usage, optimize content, fix bugs</li>
            <li>Marketing: Send promotional emails (you can opt out anytime)</li>
            <li>Legal compliance: Comply with laws, enforce our Terms, prevent fraud</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">3. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
          <p>If you are in the European Economic Area (EEA), UK, or Switzerland, we process your data under the following legal bases:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Contract performance: To provide the Service you subscribed to</li>
            <li>Legitimate interests: To improve the Service, analyze usage, and communicate with you</li>
            <li>Consent: For marketing emails (you can withdraw consent anytime)</li>
            <li>Legal obligation: To comply with laws and regulations</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
          <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Service Providers: Stripe (payments), email providers (e.g., SendGrid), analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics), hosting services</li>
            <li>Legal Requirements: If required by law, court order, or to protect our rights</li>
            <li>Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide the Service and comply with legal obligations. Specifically:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Active accounts: Data retained while your subscription is active</li>
            <li>Canceled accounts: Data retained for up to 12 months after cancellation (for support, legal, or tax purposes)</li>
            <li>Transaction records: Retained for 7 years (tax and accounting compliance)</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on your location, you may have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Access: Request a copy of your personal data</li>
            <li>Correction: Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Deletion: Request deletion of your data (subject to legal obligations)</li>
            <li>Portability: Receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
            <li>Objection: Object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
            <li>Restrict processing: Request limitation of data processing</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent: Withdraw consent for marketing emails</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 font-bold text-white">To exercise your rights:</p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:alt@altcutman.com" class="text-gold-400 hover:underline">alt@altcutman.com</a></p>
          <p class="mb-6">WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/64212550493" class="text-gold-400 hover:underline">+64 21 255 0493</a></p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">7. Security</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-6">
            <li>Encryption (SSL/TLS) for data in transit</li>
            <li>Secure hosting infrastructure</li>
            <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
            <li>Regular security audits</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-6 italic">However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">8. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4">
            <li>Remember your login and preferences</li>
            <li>Analyze site traffic and usage</li>
            <li>Personalize content</li>
            <li>Improve performance</li>
          </ul>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-white mt-4">Types of Cookies</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mb-4">
            <li>Essential cookies: Required for the Service to function</li>
            <li>Analytics cookies: Help us understand how you use the Service (e.g., Google Analytics)</li>
            <li>Marketing cookies: Used for targeted advertising (if applicable)</li>
          </ul>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-white mt-4">Managing Cookies</h4>
          <p class="mb-6">You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect functionality.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">The Service may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., YouTube, Stripe). We are not responsible for their privacy practices. Please review their privacy policies.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">The Service is not intended for children under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors. If you believe we have collected such data, please contact us immediately.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">11. International Data Transfers</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Your data may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own, including New Zealand and the United States (where our service providers are located). We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place (e.g., Standard Contractual Clauses for GDPR compliance).</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">12. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of material changes via email or through the Service. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-gold-400 mt-10 mb-4">13. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact:</p>
          
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 p-6 rounded-lg mt-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-white mb-1">Altcutm LLC</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-4">Data Protection Officer: Patrick Altcutman Musson</p>
            
            <p class="mb-1"><span class="text-gold-500 font-medium">Email:</span> <a href="mailto:alt@altcutman.com" class="hover:text-white">alt@altcutman.com</a></p>
            <p class="mb-1"><span class="text-gold-500 font-medium">WhatsApp:</span> <a href="https://wa.me/64212550493" class="hover:text-white">+64 21 255 0493</a></p>
            <p><span class="text-gold-500 font-medium">Address:</span> Mount Maunganui, Tauranga, New Zealand</p>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-neutral-500">By using AI Agency School, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
